                    <div class="testimonial-card"><div class="stars" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles"><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.123-6.545L.489 6.91l6.572-.955L10 0l2.939 5.955 6.572.955-4.756 4.635 1.123 6.545z"/></svg><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.123-6.545L.489 6.91l6.572-.955L10 0l2.939 5.955 6.572.955-4.756 4.635 1.123 6.545z"/></svg><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.123-6.545L.489 6.91l6.572-.955L10 0l2.939 5.955 6.572.955-4.756 4.635 1.123 6.545z"/></svg><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.123-6.545L.489 6.91l6.572-.955L10 0l2.939 5.955 6.572.955-4.756 4.635 1.123 6.545z"/></svg><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.123-6.545L.489 6.91l6.572-.955L10 0l2.939 5.955 6.572.955-4.756 4.635 1.123 6.545z"/></svg></div><p class="testimonial-text">"Absolument conquise ! L'odeur est subtile et agréable, et la texture pénètre rapidement sans laisser de film gras. Je recommande à 100%."</p><footer class="customer-name">- Sarah L.</footer></div>
